Lufs version 0.16
=================

This is perlufs, a perl plug for lufs.
It allows you to write filesystem implementations in perl.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Build.PL 
   ./Build
   ./Build test
   ./Build install

   # the lufs patch:
   cd lufs-0.9.7
   patch -p0 < lufs-0.97-patch.diff
   make
   make install

USAGE

For usage information, consult the Lufs(3pm) manpage.
For programming examples, see the Lufs::Howto(3pm) manpage.

DEPENDENCIES

You need a recent version of lufs (http://lufs.sf.net), with the included patch applied.

SEE ALSO

http://datamoeras.org/perlufs

